                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Calathgars are healed by cold. Anytime a calathgar would take cold damage, it instead regains [[/r 1d6 #Hit Points]]{1d6 Hit Points} (regardless of the amount of damage the cold effect would have caused).</p>\n<p>In severe cold or colder environments,9 calathgars gain @Compendium[pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.Fast Healing]{Fast Healing} 1.</p>"
