                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The calathgar expels thorny, frozen seeds in a 15-foot cone, dealing [[/r 1d6 #piercing]]{1d6 piercing damage} and [[/r 4d6 #cold]]{4d6 cold damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-traits=\"cold,evocation,primal,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Seed Spray DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save).</p>\n<p>In mild cold or colder environments, these seeds cling to living creatures they strike, dealing [[/r 1d4 #persistent cold]] @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Persistent Damage]{Persistent Cold Damage}.</p>\n<p>The calathgar can't use Seed Spray again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
